    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Vice President Al Gore and Gov. George W. Bush will debate tonight at 9:00 in the final encounter of the campaign. The event at Washington University in St. Louis will be shown live, in its entirety, on ABC, CBS, C-Span, CNN, the Fox News Channel, MSNBC and PBS.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Vice President Al Gore and Gov. George W. Bush will debate tonight at 9:00 in the final encounter of the campaign. The event at Washington University in St. Louis will be shown live, in its entirety, on ABC, CBS, C-Span, CNN, the Fox News Channel, MSNBC and PBS.</p>
        <p>NBC will not show the debate because it will be broadcasting the sixth game of the American League playoffs.</p>
        <p>THE 2000 CAMPAIGN</p>
      </block>
